<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/476003-i-have-read-this-book-every-year-since">I have read this book every year since 1973.

I would like to hear from those readers who have read both the original version in French as well as Becker&#39;s translation. I understand that by its very nature the answer to my question must be subjective: but, is the original French version as beautifully written as the Becker translation?</a>
