        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer23683534" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10246344356300336244">All I can say is that this book made me weep. Literally. If you read this book and are unmoved by the terrible inhumanity we are all capable of exhibiting, you may not have experienced a healthy dose of love in your life and therefore have no heart. Seriously. This book follows the Jewish experience through pograms to an entire family&apos;s extinction during the Holocaust. It examines anti-semitism and an all-too-human reaction to atrocity of &quot;not my problem.&quot; It is tough to read, but worth it.</span>
  <span id="freeText10246344356300336244" style="display:none">All I can say is that this book made me weep. Literally. If you read this book and are unmoved by the terrible inhumanity we are all capable of exhibiting, you may not have experienced a healthy dose of love in your life and therefore have no heart. Seriously. This book follows the Jewish experience through pograms to an entire family's extinction during the Holocaust. It examines anti-semitism and an all-too-human reaction to atrocity of "not my problem." It is tough to read, but worth it.</span>
