      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/245453-le-dernier-des-justes">Quotes from The Last of the Just</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;It is night at the front, a shadow, a shot. The Jew who has just fired<br />hears a moan...<br />"And then, mother, the hair stands up on his head, for only a few feet from him in the darkness the enemy voice is reciting in Hebrew the prayer of the dying. Ai, God, the soldier has cut down a Jewish brother! Ai, misery! He drops his rifle and runs into no man's land, insane with shame and grief. Insane, you understand? The enemy fires at him, his comrades shout at him to come back. But he refuses; he stays in no man's land and dies. Ai, misery, ai...!&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/776205-it-is-night-at-the-front-a-shadow-a-shot">2 likes</a>
            </nobr>
